name: Vacant
description:
Our presence and other’s: these concepts has always been intertwined together with its counterpart called absence. Sometimes, it fills and at times it fled from the void inside our hearts. As the cycle moves, the process liquifies many vivid images inside our heads— Melting the sharpness into nothing but a mush of blurs. We realize that this vacant space inside each of us was never really empty all along— Just like the blurred pictures which are not easily seen, but never really loses any of the colors within.  

‘Vacant’ is our musical interpretation of Yohanna Wulan’s ‘Substance of Absence’ photo series.

Artist: Jemala 
Title: Vacant
Visual: Yohanna Wulan
Format: 1080p MP4 with 320kbps stereo audio 
Duration: 01:26
